<TD WIDTH=475 ALIGN=LEFT>

Updated 10/96<p>
Listed below are the individuals with chief responsibility for the education of the gifted at
the state level throughout the United States.  State Directors serve as an information
resource concerning public school services for gifted students in their respective states. 
For information, contact the individual listed for your state.<p>


