  EJ404894  CG537125<BR>
  Family Strengths in the Care of Handicapped Children: Targets for 
Intervention.<BR>
  McCubbin, Marilyn A.; Huang, S. T. Tina<BR>
  Family Relations, v38 n4 p436-43 Oct   1989<BR>
  Available From: UMI<BR>
  Language: English<BR>
  Document Type: JOURNAL ARTICLE (080);  RESEARCH REPORT (143)<BR>
  Journal Announcement: CIJAUG90<BR>
  Investigated 130 2-parent families with children who had mild, moderate, or 
