  ED276162  EC190914<BR>
  Handi Helps, 1985<BR>
  Colorado State Univ., Ft. Collins. Cooperative Extension Service.<BR>
  Handi Helps, Jan-Apr, Oct-Dec 1985;  14p.<BR>
  EDRS Price - MF01/PC01 Plus Postage.<BR>
  Language: English<BR>
  Document Type: SERIAL (022);  NON-CLASSROOM MATERIAL (055)<BR>
  Geographic Source: U.S.; Colorado<BR>
