</TABLE> 
 

<table width=600>
<tr><td width=200 valign=top><b>GTOT-L</b><br></td><td width=400><b>    
Topics related to very young children (generally under<br> 6 years of age) who are gifted</b><BR>
<font size=2> Subscription address:       listproc@eskimo.com<BR>
                     Post messages to:            gtot-l@eskimo.com<BR>
</font></td></tr>
<tr><td width=200 valign=top><b>Giftednet-l</b><br></td><td width=400>
<b>            National (USA) Science and Language Arts <br> Curriculum Projects for High Ability Learners</b><BR><font size=2>Note that mailing 
list name ends in lowercase "ell" not numeral 1.  Also note that the 
William and Mary curriculum now has its own limited distribution list 
(WMCURRIC-L).<br>
Subscription address:    listserver@listserv.cc.wm.edu<BR>
                     Post messages to:            GiftedNet@cc.wm.edu<BR>
