Irving, TX 75015-2079;<BR>
Tel: 214/580-2000; <A HREF="http://www.bsa.scouting.org">BSA Headquarters</A></B><BR>
</P>

<P><B>Girl Scouts of the U.S.A., 420 Fifth Avenue, New York, NY 10018-2798;<BR>
Tel: 800/247-8319; <A HREF="http://www.gsusa.org">GS U.S.A. Headquarters
Web Page</A> ; E-mail GS U.S.A.</B><BR>
